{"tid":1819143,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"資本主義 vs共產主義","createTime":"2020-01-10T14:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T14:44:55.000Z","uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"def27b6ae95432566d37a5ec3a769bdd81e6e30a","tid":1819143,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:02:14.000Z","msg":"資本主義下就一定會有人賺多啲 有人賺少啲<br />\n如果政府冇乜干預 有錢人就可以利用自身優勢<br />\n將兩班人推向極端 貧者越貧 富者越富<br />\n所以依家世界上1%既人擁有99%財富<br />\n容易造成仇富現象<br />\n例如社會上有班人想好似共產黨上台時咁鬥地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n共產主義相信大家都好熟悉<br />\n做又36 唔做又36<br />\n所有野歸啊公 &quot;公平分配&quot;<br />\n所以好易養懶人<br />\n亦因為咁啲人冇動力去創新<br />\n長遠對社會一定造成負面影響<br />\n<br />\n大家支持邊隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e24d1de3246bea21565c5a576f30a36823cbe9","tid":1819143,"uid":315626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"好似有套制度係行資本+極重税極高福利 幾中意果套"},{"pid":"df10f8b57db4fbe450b013a701dd3f6edc7bb39c","tid":1819143,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"公平分配<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗱，我收走99.9%「保持社會運作手續費」先<br />\n果0.1%我會平均分配㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055fb5b4d034e63402ceff4d46379f00416c41b0","tid":1819143,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"應該實行<br />\n多勞多得 公平原則"},{"pid":"1f9ff9c3100b0af6039ff3e63d2ac2eef4c1b7e3","tid":1819143,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n並存架<br />\n世界上無一個國家係完全資本／共產<br />\n抽稅做社福其實係共產concept<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"85e6f9cce86b8f8ddeda175104a5092f96ffc92a","tid":1819143,"uid":105018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"